title: Don’t Get Me Wrong, I’m The Real Victim!
description: Don’t Get Me Wrong, I’m The Real Victim! Manhua An abandoned factory in the middle of the night, an impressive haunted house in an amusement park, and a grim smiling mask above a bloody white coat roaming every dark corner of the city. It has witnessed every single heinous crime, but please don’t get me wrong, I’m only a victim. Bie Wuhui, Wo Cai Shi Shouhai Zhe! Bié Wùhuì, Wǒ Cái Shì Shòuhài Zhě! Don’t Get Me Wrong, I Am the Victim! Don’t Misunderstand, I Am the Victim! 别误会，我才是受.. 别误会，我才是受害者！
